brainly_data.question: Distension of the ureter, or this term, can be a result of a ureteral calculus. what is this term?
brainly_data.subject: Health

all_answers.question: Distension of the ureter, or this term, can be a result of a ureteral calculus. what is this term?
all_answers.subject: Health
all_answers.text: The answer is Ureterectasis which means the distension of the ureter or can be a result of a ureteral calculus. A ureteral obstruction is the blockage in the ureters, the one carrying the urine from the kidney to the bladder yet this can be curable.
